member.returns:
The implicit context associated with this communicator;
            returns null when the property Ice.ImplicitContext is not set
            or is set to None.

If the operation was invoked synchronously (because there
           was no need to queue the request), the return value is true;
           otherwise, if the invocation was queued, the return value is false.

